Flowering Hill[/b], the Realm of Sheela Peryroyl, resembles a quiet agricultural community populated by halfling Petitioners. Many of the homes here are built into the roots of living trees. It is located in the Outlands, spireward of the Gate-town of Ecstasy. 
Source[/b]
Planescape Campaign Setting (poster map)
A Player's Primer to the Outlands
On Hallowed Ground